Raise xtest global retry budget to 10

CI has been seeing pipeline runs fail outright once more than 3 tests
flake in a single run, since RETRY_BUDGET capped total retries across
the whole suite regardless of how many distinct tests flaked. Raise
the budget to 10 so a handful of unrelated flakes don't sink a run.

Per-test retry count (XTEST_RETRIES, default 1) is unchanged.
